{"tid":1675570,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"中國抗體製藥闖關　短期內招股","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:45:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T04:33:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f56712aeaa4a1bd63918ffa9253e86393b35c9c","tid":1675570,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:45:24.000Z","msg":"尚未有盈利或收入生物科技公司中國抗體製藥已通過上市聆訊，消息人士透露，公司已進行預路演，是次集資1.5億美元至2億美元(約11.7億港元至15.6億港元)，計劃下周至11月初招股，11月內掛牌上市。<br />\n該公司為專門研究、發展、製造及商業化自身免疫性疾病療法的香港生物製藥公司，主要研製以單克隆抗體為基礎的生物藥。計劃集資所得用於研發及商業化其核心產品；用於建設蘇州生產基地；以及用作營運資金等。<br />\n<br />\n據聆訊後更新的文件，截至今年4月底止4個月，虧損2,839.8萬元人民幣(下同)，去年同期蝕2,379.5萬元；研發開支2,020.9萬元，按年增加51.14%。2018年全年虧損8361萬元人民幣；研發開支4,728.3萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191025/mobile/bkn-20191025222758265-1025_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20191025%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191025222758265-1025_00842_001.html&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN82proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=6df06cc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20191025/mobile/bkn-20191025222758265-1025_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n雲南白藥做基投，大家看來都會玩多次"},{"pid":"3f810ff36cab6ba1a9cfbce9a6b66550f3821ccf","tid":1675570,"uid":172026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:55:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中金系，不了！"},{"pid":"e19058d938234b77e5384643cb71e82af8b16aa2","tid":1675570,"uid":39520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"炒炒炒"},{"pid":"3a4690f683365b0fb0a57e4691c61fd5193c1984","tid":1675570,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:33:35.000Z","msg":"<ins><span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10.26 (六)</span></strong></span></ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YjEwyoq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2